{"tid":2452942,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"絲打入 平時m痛點搞","createTime":"2021-03-19T06:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T16:26:43.000Z","uid":258112,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"88de8a44f4cfc22ad9344e773ac6b0e5f3a137de","tid":2452942,"uid":258112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:51:49.000Z","msg":"次次period頭兩日都痛到仆街<br />\n好似個子宮俾人揸爆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n飲熱水薑茶會好少少<br />\n但係都會陰啲陰啲痛<br />\n<br />\n然後就索性食止痛藥<br />\n次次period平均食5粒咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔想成日食依賴藥<br />\n但係真係好撚痛<br />\n一係就痛到落唔到床做唔到野<br />\n一係就陰啲陰啲痛 但係都專心唔到<br />\n<br />\n我知戒凍野先係最有用嘅方法<br />\n但係真係好無意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗咁就戒曬凍 甜品 雪糕<br />\n不如打死我算<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef124ec56b702eac34d37f4e082ae51182dc8272","tid":2452942,"uid":239709,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:52:20.000Z","msg":"食兩支煙"},{"pid":"64684cedd3db94764631491fa95360535668e1c3","tid":2452942,"uid":40272,"like":21,"dislike":8,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:53:02.000Z","msg":"搵我射兩督精入去"},{"pid":"dce846664a21b2ba5b361430ca487741e15097f2","tid":2452942,"uid":306907,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:55:13.000Z","msg":"有幾個月好乖咁 戒咗凍飲嗌熱飲 但係都係好撚痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea62f8969b08d8a45c959781b41674101fee9fff","tid":2452942,"uid":7656,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"買包嗰啲暖宮貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：成日買俾女朋友"},{"pid":"785922082c17bdf125f0f24de606416a13f676db","tid":2452942,"uid":180019,"like":1,"d