ets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e002cd2dec36ff4d09b004e3128f9438ac4eefb","tid":2452942,"uid":178548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"我頭2日會痛但最多集中唔到<br />\n第3日唔痛<br />\n有時第4日突然朝早好痛好痛<br />\n痛到要即刻食藥唔係好似要死咁<br />\n食完過10分鐘又無野之後就唔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052cddfe52869e750649f3760c2502c1d1f2d6db","tid":2452942,"uid":3272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dc4a2614e1cbcc5a92ae35008f554d16a41c6b7","tid":2452942,"uid":138197,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:57:01.000Z","msg":"我有個方法可以令你唔M痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"hugo1991?"},{"pid":"f394976d79f10923e9a32686730c4b708d844319","tid":2452942,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:08:35.000Z","msg":"有冇做開運動？<br />\n我之前都好痛 養成運動習慣之後就冇乜點再痛"},{"pid":"c0d410eaf39c55bdeb8773a4431a289771f66ebb","tid":2452942,"uid":1191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:11:12.000Z","msg":"你同我一齊我保你十個月唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0fbf0cdd1695a47578127df9314e93fa3a39a2","tid":2452942,"uid":94465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"早啲訓"},{"pid":"e707023f478e44a2f3b12de6be163b05b8ee966a","tid":2452942,"uid":81657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"建議搵醫生照下"},{"pid":"ba646c53ab4bbee2dcead380f88ec01abfa9f5bc","tid":2452942,"uid":390185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"平時飲暖水 黎完m會飲當歸紅棗湯（老母會煲）<br />\n我除咗黎m屙屎會勁肚痛外 都無咩痛"},{"pid":"2092e61260d903800e65cdb89f3f16352936af26","tid":2452942,"uid":352218,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"太痛真係要去照ultrasound&hellip;<br />\n有朋友照完confirm有子宮肌瘤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用冬天貼衫果d暖包 (暖宮貼太貴)<br />\n搽&quot;經月爽&quot; (辣到hihi&hellip;冬天用好爽&hellip;但千祈唔好夾埋暖包一齊用, 會好刺痛) <br />\nM到前7日睇中醫&hellip;連續飲兩至三日藥 (work但一停咗唔飲又痛過)<br />\nM到前幾日飲玫瑰茶幫助排血<br />\n唔好亂飲薑茶因為有d人體質(熱底) 唔受得會搞到有血塊<br />\n少飲凍野、少食生冷野 (尤其M前一星期&hellip;否則落地獄嘅痛) <br />\n做多d運動 (要時間先見效)<br />\n食止痛藥真係最後忍唔到先好食&hellip;因為真係好傷身<br />\n<br />\n祝各絲打有個健康的子宮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630a4e98f5dff77438c3debda50e7c2625d29a77","tid":2452942,"uid":258112,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"2092e61260d903800e65cdb89f3f16352936af26","tid":2452942,"uid":352218,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"太痛真係要去照ultrasound&hellip;<br />\n有朋友照完confirm有子宮肌瘤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用冬天貼衫果d暖包 (暖宮貼太貴)<br />\n搽&quot;經月爽&quot; (辣到hihi&hellip;冬天用好爽&hellip;但千祈唔好夾埋暖包一齊用, 會好刺痛) <br />\nM到前7日睇中醫&hellip;連續飲兩至三日藥 (work但一停咗唔飲又痛過)<br />\nM到前幾日飲玫瑰茶幫助排血<br />\n唔好亂飲薑茶因為有d人體質(熱底) 唔受得會搞到有血塊<br />\n少飲凍野、少食生冷野 (尤其M前一星期&hellip;否則落地獄嘅痛) <br />\n做多d運動 (要時間先見效)<br />\n食止痛藥真係最後忍唔到先好食&hellip;因為真係好傷身<br />\n<br />\n祝各絲打有個健康的子宮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T16:46:12.000Z","msg":"戒咁多野 人生好無意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要每月一星期<br />\n不斷循環 真係不了"},{"pid":"5833f3aba69d16039ab8fe2758efd8c05787abd2","tid":2452942,"uid":229169,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T18:07:26.000Z","msg":"試下做下運動？跑下步又好就咁拉下筋活動下又好<br />\n我中、大學做開運動<br />\n來M完全唔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢兩年冇乜點做運動就開始來m會痛<br />\n唔知關唔關事 但第一日真係生不如死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2459fd4403dacfacedf14d1200875784f155d7c","tid":2452942,"uid":197584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T00